Description

Product ID: 482296

  • Heavy-weight cotton jersey fabric with a smooth feel and a laid-back look. A durable and long-lasting fabric made of thick yarn.

    Binding at the collar helps the neckline keep its shape. Neckline inspired by vintage military T-shirt designs.

    Uniqlo U

    View the full collection

  • Made from high-quality cotton, this crew neck T-shirt from the Uniqlo U collection offers exceptional softness and durability for everyday wear. Its classic design provides a clean, timeless look that pairs effortlessly with any outfit, making it a versatile essential for your wardrobe. Designed for comfort and style, this tee delivers a flattering fit and elevated simplicity for any occasion.

    - Crafted from high-quality cotton for softness and durability.
    - Classic crew neck design for a timeless, versatile look.
    - Part of the Uniqlo U collection, known for elevated basics.
    - Easy to style with jeans, trousers, or layered under jackets.
    - Available in a range of neutral and seasonal colors.

    - The images shown may include colors that are not available.

    Product ID: 482296,475356,471583,465186

  • Production

    Production: Bangladesh, Cambodia, Viet Nam

    Our brand is continuously working to improve our understanding of the production process in our supply chain and to verify this information both in-house and with third parties. By having full understanding of the origins of raw materials, and the locations of the spinning, material production, sewing, knitting, and assembly processes, we are improving quality of our clothing and at the same time aiming to thoroughly ensure safe and secure manufacturing. We will continue to post information for customers to access and learn more about their clothing.

    *The information on material production locations applies to products manufactured after 24FW.

    Do Not Sell My Personal Information

    The California Consumer Policy Act ("CCPA") provides consumer with specific rights regarding their personal information. If you live in California, under the CCPA you have the right to opt-out of the sale of your personal information. Please use the toggle below, as well as the information found in our Privacy Policy, to opt-out of the sale of your personal Information.

    Strictly Necessary Cookies

    Always Active

    These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

    Performance Cookies

    Always Active

    These cookies allow us to collect information about the traffic on our website and the technical performance of the website. They help us to get detailed and advanced analytics. In some cases these cookies improve the speed with which we can process your request, allow us to remember site preferences you've selected. This includes cookies from third-party analytics services.

    Functional Cookies

    Always Active

    These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.

    Targeting Cookies

    These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
